description.en:
Swing King swing hook

With this swing hook you simply hang your swings. Because of the zinc coating, the swing will not rust. This durable swing hook is suitable for mounting on square posts.

Specifications:
Colour: gold
Gender: junior
Material: galvanized steel
Fixation: square posts
Dimensions: 90 x 90 mm
Thickness: 3 mm

Geschlecht: junior
Material: verzinkter Stahl
Befestigung: quadratische Pfosten
Abmessungen: 90 x 90 mm
